title: 9/26/17 - Meet America's New Icon? (Kitty Higgins & Burgess Owens join Glenn)
description:
The Dallas Cowboys are an example for America ...Donald Trump's USFL days ...Flashback to 1985: Trump vs. NFL ...Meet America's new icon...Alejandro Villanueva ...NFL great Burgess Owens joins the show to give his perspective on what's going on in the NFL ...Another email scandal in the making? ...Red dots, blue dots, green dots, oh my! ...Russia was paying for ads for 'Black Lives Matter' ...Where Putin agrees with President Lincoln.

The Glenn Beck Program with Glenn Beck, Pat Gray, Stu Burguiere and Jeff Fisher, Weekdays 9a–12pm ET on TheBlaze Radio
